ACCESSING ACTION LOG...

>You are an ordinary Anon. The kind who has frequented /scp/ for a while now. Enough that you're desperate to see Mal0 in reality.
>One night, you decide to try and find the app and download it. To your delight, you manage to find it and install it; albeit, from your laptop to your phone.
>Everything proceeded as it did in every Mal0 green you've read. The texts. The images slowly getting closer.
>Everything... except Mal0 herself.
>The huge, lanky, furry creature stared with luminous yellow eyes. Her skull grinned at you ghoulishly as she leaned into your face.
>Where shaggy black fur should've been was instead smooth fur of a deep scarlet. Rather than eyesockets with pearly white lights, she had yellow eyes that glittered mischievously. Her teeth were far more jagged and sharp-looking than what the greens suggested.
>This... wasn't Mal0.
>"Heh. I guess I'm n0t what y0u expected?"
>"Y-you're... not Mal0."
>The creature laughed hoarsely.
>"0f c0urse I am, numbskull. N0t the 0ne y0u've been dr00ling 0ver th0ugh. I'm m0dded."
>"What?"
>She put on a condescending smile.
>"M0-dded, m0r0n. Like a vide0game? S0me l0nely hacker cust0mized my app. And s0meh0w y0u g0t the wr0ng file. C0ngratulati0ns, idi0t; y0u're stuck with me n0w."
>"W-what do I call you?"
>"Mal0. 0bvi0usly. If y0u wanna call me s0mething else, g0 f0r it."
>Your eyes scanned her body once more. Claws long enough to gore you adorned her hands and feet. A long, bushy tail swept back and forth behind her.
>Her lean torso carried the weight of two colossal breasts, each tipped with a black nipple. Her skull was perfectly white, as if bleached. She smiled at you lasciviously.
>"Like what y0u see...? H0pe s0; I'm y0urs~"

[BITE OFF YOUR TONGUE AND CHOKE ON IT]

>You perform the only logical action:
>You bite off and intentionally choke yourself with your tongue.
>You are dead.

RESTART
