>Reflected in the ice crystals, with stunning clarity, are your faces.  Human, skull-beast, and shroomcat.  All shown brilliantly in each crystal of each snowflake.
>It's truly a gorgeous sight.
>Suddenly, Pyr3 and Percy pull you close.  The three of you share a warm, cozy embrace for what feels like years.
>The snow remains still around you, reflecting your mutual love for one another.
>The sheer comfort you feel is immeasurable.
>Eventually, you slowly fall to the ground.  Upon landing, the three of you begin making snow angels.
>You find that your head is resting on a pleasantly soft snowdrift...

>...you awaken to find your head laying comfortably on Pyr3's plush ass.
>You quickly assess the situation:
>The three of you somehow ended up in the floor.  Pyr3 is asleep on her stomach, snoring.
>As you already know, you are resting on your back, with your head on her rear.  For a moment, you are unable to find Percy.
>Then, you notice the purring, and a weight atop your chest.
>Percy is curled up on top of you, sleeping peacefully.  The tags in her ear glint in the light, and her tail twitches occasionally.
>You are extremely comfortable, even despite Percy's weight atop you.

[DO NOT DISTURB]

>Seeing as you're comfortable, and they're still asleep, you see no need to disturb the current situation.
>You merely lay your head back down on Pyr3's supple, firm backside.
>The soft, lush fur feels wonderful against the back of your neck.  Her steady breathing assures you that she's sleeping soundly.
>The dim light dances off of her skull in an almost ethereal manner.  It's quite a beautiful sight, in an odd way.
>You take a deep breath, taking in the warm, comforting scent of cinnamon.  Pyr3 unconsciously drapes her tail across your face.
>Meanwhile, Percy unconsciously adjusts her position, her claws gently grabbing your shirt as she does so.
>She smiles in her sleep, and her purring never ceases.
>As she lays there, she occasionally rubs her head against your chest, her ears twitching.  You're tempted to stroke her cap, but think better of it.  You don't want to wake her.
>Considering that she's a tad taller than you, Percy isn't all that heavy.  You suppose that's due to her decade of isolation.  She can't have eaten well, trapped in that lab.
>You make it a point to keep taking care of her, as well as Pyr3.

[KISS THE BUTT]

>Being extra careful not to wake either of the two up, you crane your neck around to get a good view of your makeshift pillow.
>While Pyr3's prodigious bust is perhaps the most immediately notable part of her, you must admit she also has quite a bit going on back here.
>Her firm, inviting ass causes your mouth to water a bit.
>...you give in to some deep part of your psyche and plant a kiss on one of her red-furred cheeks.
>She doesn't appear to notice, thankfully.
>However...
>With a yawn, Percy awakens.
>She rises onto all fours, still atop you, and stretches much like an ordinary cat.
