>Pyr3 eyes up Sumner with a distrustful look.  You get the impression she's scanning him for any weaknesses should things go south.
>You can't help but notice that she has picked up a large rock, presumably just in case she needs a blunt weapon.  She glances your way, golden eyes narrowed and pupils contracted into slits.
>At least it's not just you.

[QUERY]

