>"Sumner, I don't quite understand your vision from earlier.  Are you trying to... expand the forest?"
>Another pause.  You get the sensation that he's rather awkwardly thinking of what to "say".
>An extremely tiny tree grows and rots away.  You suppose that's the equivalent to a very sheepish yes.
>"...how?"
