>"That was pretty fun, but it's g00d t0 be h0me.  Whaddya say we just huddle up f0r a while, have s0me dinner later?"
>"Sounds good to me."
>ME TOO
>Pyr3 yawns again, and gently repositions herself, lying down.  Percy snuggles even closer to you, her purring intensifying.
>Between the smells of cinnamon and sweet spores, as well as the warmth of the ladies' fur, you feel extremely cozy and above all...
>Safe.
>That episode with Summer could've gone bad in an instant.  You're extremely grateful that Pyr3 and Percy were there for you.  And to think that you expected Percy's disguise failing to be the only possible risk...
>You glance at the clock.  Nearly dinner time, but you've got a while to just enjoy the girls' company.  You're not sleepy, but Pyr3 looks like she might doze off.

[COOK DINNER]
GAME SAVED

>Almost immediately, Pyr3 confirms your suspicions by dozing off.  She snores loudly, and Percy snickers.
>LAZYBONES
>You smile down at the sleeping beast and gently pull a blanket over her.  Then, you carefully get up and sneak into the kitchen, with your fungal friend following.
>"Want to help me with dinner?  I'm making hamburgers."
>Percy nods eagerly, her tail twitching wildly.  She scrambles over to the counter and waits patiently.
>With her watching closely, you pat out some burgers.  She eyes up your handiwork with obvious enthusiasm.
>You season up two of the burgers, and let Percy handle her own.
>Unsurprisingly, she yanks a mushroom off of her side and crumbles it over her food.  She smiles proudly, and you gently pat her cap encouragingly.
>As the burgers cook, the sweet scent of the mushroom fills your kitchen.  Percy purrs loudly as she enjoys the aroma.
>Personally, you don't particularly enjoy the combination of sweet and meaty scents.

[SAUTEE MUSHROOMS]

>You can't help but smile at Percy's happiness.
>"So, how was your first day out?"
>I LOVED IT
>HAD A LOT OF FUN 
>EVEN THOUGH I DIDN'T LIKE SUMNER
>"Yeah, uh... he kinda creeped me out too, a little.  Glad you enjoyed yourself though."
>THANK YOU FOR TAKING ME WITH YOU
>She suddenly wraps her arms around you, hugging you tightly.  You return the gesture.
>When she releases you, you make your way to the fridge.  You just remembered buying some mushrooms the other day.
>You quickly saute them up, much to Percy's obvious excitement, and top her burger off with them.
>"Y'know, there are a lot of types of mushrooms out there.  Next time I go shopping, I'll pick you up some to try."
>THANK YOU, I'D LIKE THAT
>"Thought you might, heh."
>You pat her cap, with her enthusiastically leaning into your pats.

[SERVE DINNER]
GAME SAVED

>Eventually, dinner is ready to serve.
>"Percy, can you go wake Pyr3 up before her food gets cold?"
>Without so much as writing a word, the cat dashes off into the living room.
>Before long, she returns, following a drowsy Pyr3.
>"Mm?  W-where's the fire?  Did y0u need s0methin'?"
>You chuckle.
>"No, dinner's done and I didn't want your burger getting cold."
>At the mention of dinner, the skull headed beast immediately perks up.
>"00h!  Why didn't ya say s0?  Let's dig in."
>She quickly makes her way to the table, with Percy following behind.
>Once they're seated, you serve up everyone's food, making sure to give Percy her personalized burger.
>True to form, Pyr3 scarfs down her dinner in minutes.  You pace yourself, but still finish before your fungal friend.
>She seems to savor every last bite, smiling proudly.  When she finally finishes, she excitedly scribbles another message.
>I HELPED MAKE THAT!
>Pyr3 smiles warmly.
>"Really?  That's great."
>Percy beams at her crimson-furred friend.

[SHOWER]

>Once dinner is finished, you begin to realize how... dirty you feel.  You HAVE spent all day in the woods, dealing with some kinda... sinister force.
>It's probably about time for a shower.
>"Hey, I'm gonna go get cleaned up real quick.  I'll be back."
>Percy waves as you head off to the bathroom...
>But Pyr3 follows you.
>"Heh.  I'm with y0u: I need a sh0wer."
>Once you're out of Percy's line of sight, Pyr3 winks at you, a wicked smile appearing.
>"H0w b0ut we share a sh0wer, save s0me water, eh~?"
>You don't even attempt to protest.  Once you reach the bathroom, the red-furred woman steps under the shower and turns it on.
>The water cascades off of her beautifully, tracing her curves tantalizingly.  She meets your eyes and winks again.
>You quickly undress and join her beneath the hot downpour.
>As soon as you do so, she presses herself against you.  Her hot, wet fur caresses your bare skin wonderfully.  Her bountiful chest is squeezed between the two of you.
